        "Windows Apps|seven:windows apps|Open Bottles for Windows applications"
        "Windows VM|seven:windows vm|Open Virt Manager for Windows desktop mode"
        "Windows Mode Start|seven:windows start|Start SevenOS Windows VM"
        "Windows Mode Console|seven:windows console|Open SevenOS Windows VM console"
        "Install WINDOWS|windows|Install Wine, Lutris, QEMU, Bottles"
        "VM Check|vm-check|Check KVM and libvirt readiness"
        "VM Network|vm-network|Start libvirt default network"
        "Open Virt Manager|app:virt-manager|Launch VM manager"
        "Open Bottles|app:flatpak run com.usebottles.bottles|Launch Bottles"
      )
      ;;
    "Server & Deploy")
      actions=(
        "Server Status|seven:server status|Show SevenOS local API readiness"
        "Server Doctor|seven:server doctor|Check deployment dependencies"
        "Install Server Layer|server|Install server and deployment packages"
        "Install User Service|seven:server install-user-service|Install seven-server user service"
        "Start Server|seven:server start|Start local SevenOS API"
        "Stop Server|seven:server stop|Stop local SevenOS API"
        "Deploy Status|seven:deploy status|Show generated deployment plans"
        "Deploy Current Project|seven:deploy .|Generate a plan for this repository"
